    "description": "Yum! Brands India is actively seeking a talented and motivated Reservation Manager to join our dynamic team in Bhubaneswar. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Yum! Brands India:\nYum! Brands India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Yum! Brands India!",
